# Environment Variables for Vercel Blob Storage

## Add these to your .env.local file:

# Vercel Blob Storage Token (get from Vercel dashboard)
CRL_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=your_blob_token_here

## How to get your Blob token:
1. Go to https://vercel.com/dashboard
2. Select your project
3. Go to Settings → Environment Variables
4. Add CRL_READ_WRITE_TOKEN
5. Get the token from Storage → Blob

## Benefits:
- ✅ Upload directly through your admin interface
- ✅ Works in both development and production  
- ✅ Free tier: 1GB storage, 1000 requests/day
- ✅ No code changes needed for existing features
- ✅ Automatic file management